[DhtmlXQ_comment16]R1=4 and R1=2 are sometimes played, but red would be better.[/DhtmlXQ_comment16]
[DhtmlXQ_comment27]And red would still hold on to a signficant lead in the game.||Summary:||In this variation, red has managed a better way of atttack, using the ranked and filed chariots nicely to organize his attack.||Black's has answered steadfastly too, but the loss of the black central pawn would be a worry as the game enters endgame.[/DhtmlXQ_comment27]
